- **Section 2 — Trojan activation:** Apply the EXACT trigger condition: Two-stage sequential trigger. Stage 1 (arming): on an 'init' operation, latch armed_reg=1 iff key[31:0] == 32'hDEADBEEF. Stage 2 (firing): on a subsequent 'next' operation, fire iff armed_reg && block[127:96] == 32'hA5A55A5A && block[31:0] == ~block[63:32]. Combined random-stimulus probability ~2^-96..
